Executive Profile
Mark V. Kaminski  Chairman and Chief Executive Officer, Granite Rock CompanyAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 2 different industries.See Board Relationships61--
Background

		Mr. Mark V. Kaminski serves as the Chairman and Chief Executive Officer at Granite Rock Company. Mr. Kaminski served as the Chief Executive Officer and President of Commonwealth Industries Inc. from April 1991 to June 11, 2004. He joined Commonwealth Industries Inc. in 1987 as Marketing Manager. He served as Vice President and General Manager of Operations of Commonwealth Aluminum Corporation from 1989 to 1991 and as Industry Marketing Manager from 1987 to 1989. He joined ... Commonwealth Industries in 1987, he served in various positions at Atlantic Richfield Corporation. He has been Non-Executive Chairman of the Board of Reliance Steel & Aluminum Co. since 2016. Mr. Kaminski serves as a Director of Secat Inc. and Director of Indiana University Athletics Board. He has been Independent Lead Director at Reliance Steel & Aluminum Co. since January 15, 2015 and has been its Independent Director since November 1, 2004. He has been a Director of Granite Rock Company since June 26, 2012. He served as a Director of Commonwealth Industries, Inc. from November 1990 to 2004. He served as a Director of ARM Financial Group Inc. since September 1998. Mr. Kaminski received a B.S. Degree in Business from Indiana University and an Advanced Management degree from Harvard Business School.Read Full Background




